fulltitle: Gerry Hemingway Stone Retrospective Residency July 28 - August 2, 2015 Trailer
description:
For more information on this upcoming series of performances visit:

http://gerryhemingway.com

This is a short trailer about the week long residency of Gerry Hemingway at the Stone between July 28 and August 2, 2015.

Video produced by:  while others sleep productions 
camera: Valeria Zangger
Location: near Aemsigen, Pilatus, Luzern, Switzerland

The Complete Schedule:

Tuesday July 28 - Re-Ensemble - duos, trios, quartets and quintets

8 + 10pm 2 set program - one entrance fee for whole evening 20$

Anne LeBaron - harp, Earl Howard - electronics, alto & soprano saxophone, George Grayva - piano, Susan Alcorn - steel guitar, Gerry Hemingway - drums

Wednesday July 29 - Improvisations #1 - Trios

8pm - 15$
Anthony Coleman- piano, Marty Ehrlich - reeds, Gerry Hemingway - drums
10pm - 15$
Sporty Brown Trio revisited - Rudresh Mahanthappa - reeds, Russ Lossing - piano, Gerry Hemingway - drums

Thursday July 30 - Compositions #1 - Songs & “Riptide” Quintet

8pm - 15$
Songs with Lisa Sokolov - voice, Michael Winsch - piano, Terrence McManus - guitar, Brad Jones - el/ac bass, Ellery Eskelin - tenor saxophone, Gerry Hemingway - drums, sampler
10pm - 15$
Gerry Hemingway Quintet - Oscar Noriega - clarinet, bass clarinet, alto saxophone, Ellery Eskelin - tenor saxophone, Terrence McManus - guitar, Brad Jones - el/ac bass, Gerry Hemingway - drums, harmonica, sampler

Friday July 31 Improvisations #2 - Brew & Anew

8pm - 15$
Brew - Miya Masaoka - koto, electronics, Reggie Workman - bass, Gerry Hemingway - drums, sampler
10pm - 15$
Anew Quartet - Ned Rothenberg - reeds, Michael Winsch - piano, Mark Helias - bass, Gerry Hemingway - drums

Saturday August 1  Compositions #2  Solo & Quartet

8pm - 15$
Solo Works and Interactive Collaborations with visual artist Beth Warshafsky and composer Sarah Weaver
Gerry Hemingway - drums and sampler, Beth Warshafsky - interactive visual projection 
10pm - 15$
Gerry Hemingway Quartet - Herb Robertson - trumpet, Ellery Eskelin - tenor saxophone, Mark Helias - acoustic, electric bass, Gerry Hemingway - drums

Sunday August 2 Relationships of time

8pm - 15$
Trio NY - Ellery Eskelin-tenor saxophone, Gary Versace-organ, Gerry Hemingway - drums
10pm - 15$
BassDrumBone - Mark Helias - bass, Gerry Hemingway - drums, Ray Anderson - trombone
